Package: macIDR
Type: Package
Title: Macrophage identifier
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew Y.F. Li Yim
Maintainer: Andrew Y.F. Li Yim <andrewliyim@gmail.com>
Description: A wrapper function for utilizing the classifier models for the eight M-CSF in vitro macrophage subsets as decribed in Chen et al. 2019.
    The following macrophage subsets can be distinguished: M0, MLPSearly, MLPSlate, MLPSIFNg, MIFNg, MIL4, MIL10, and Mdex.
